item.title: This Site
item.description: I created this site to serve as my professional profile, but that was not the only reason. My other reason for creating this website was to give myself a project using git and emacs (specifically Doom Emacs) to gain some experience. The site is not content complete yet. It is mostly just a skeleton with the minimal theme at this point.
